1. Use make to compile the program and create the lander file
2. Run ./lander -t ?? -f ?? -g ?? to begin the game
3. Funcions:
	erase_old           - erase the old ship or the thrust fire 
	draw 		    - draw the ship 
	landscape 	    - draw the landscape
	hanle_signal 	    - the key signa function, every time call that, it
			      will erase the old ship firstly, and then begin 				      to update the new position of the ship, then it 				      will check if the we pressed the direction keys 				      or SPACE, at last it wil check if the ship 				      crashed or landed nad return.


